  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The speed of sound in dry air, <span class=\"italic\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic \">v</span></span>, can be modeled by the formula <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"v equals, 331 point 3 plus 0 point 6 0 6 times T\"></span></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">T</span> is the temperature in degrees Celsius and <span class=\"italic\">v</span> is measured in meters per&nbsp;second. Which of the following correctly expresses <span class=\"italic\">T</span> in terms&nbsp;of&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">v</span>&nbsp;?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<span class=\"math_expression \">\n            <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"T equals, the fraction with numerator, v plus 0 point 6 0 6, and denominator, 331 point 3\"></span></span>\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
      "content": "<span class=\"math_expression \">\n            <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"T equals, the fraction with numerator, v minus 0 point 6 0 6, and denominator, 331 point 3\"></span></span>\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "c",
      "content": "<span class=\"math_expression \">\n            <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"T equals, the fraction with numerator, v plus 331 point 3, and denominator, 0 point 6 0 6\"></span></span>\n"
